.TH "ljc" "1" "2025-12-04"
.PP
.SH NAME
.PP
ljc - LinearJC job development and deployment tool
.PP
.SH SYNOPSIS
.PP
\fBljc\fR <command> [options]
.PP
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
ljc is a command-line tool for developing, testing, and deploying LinearJC
jobs.\& It handles the full lifecycle from creating new jobs to monitoring
their execution on remote coordinators.\&
.PP
.SH COMMANDS
.PP
.SS Development
.PP
\fBinit\fR
.RS 4
Initialize a new job repository in the current directory.\&
.PP
.RE
\fBnew\fR <job-id>
.RS 4
Create a new job from template.\&
.PP
.RE
\fBinfo\fR [job-id]
.RS 4
Show job information.\&
.PP
.RE
\fBlist\fR
.RS 4
List all jobs in repository.\&
.PP
.RE
\fBvalidate\fR [job-id]
.RS 4
Validate job configuration.\&
.PP
.RE
\fBbuild\fR [job-id]
.RS 4
Build job package (.\&ljc archive).\&
.PP
.RE
\fBbump\fR <job-id> <major|minor|patch>
.RS 4
Bump job version.\&
.PP
.RE
\fBtest\fR <job-id>
.RS 4
Test job locally with optional isolation.\&
.PP
.RE
.SS Deployment
.PP
\fBsync\fR --from <broker>
.RS 4
Sync registry from coordinator.\&
.PP
.RE
\fBregistry\fR
.RS 4
Show local registry map.\&
.PP
.RE
\fBdeploy\fR <package.\&ljc> --to <broker>
.RS 4
Deploy package to coordinator.\&
.PP
.RE
.SS Runtime
.PP
\fBexec\fR <job-id> [--follow|--wait]
.RS 4
Execute job immediately, bypassing scheduler.\&
.PP
.RE
\fBtail\fR <job-id|execution-id>
.RS 4
Follow job execution progress in real-time.\&
.PP
.RE
\fBstatus\fR <job-id>|--all
.RS 4
Show job scheduling status.\&
.PP
.RE
\fBps\fR [--all] [--executor <id>]
.RS 4
List active job executions.\&
.PP
.RE
\fBlogs\fR <job-id> [--last <n>]
.RS 4
Show job execution history.\&
.PP
.RE
\fBkill\fR <execution-id> [--force]
.RS 4
Cancel a running job.\&
.PP
.RE
.SH ENVIRONMENT
.PP
\fBLINEARJC_SECRET\fR
.RS 4
Shared secret for coordinator authentication.\& Required for remote
operations.\&
.PP
.RE
\fBMQTT_BROKER\fR
.RS 4
MQTT broker hostname (default: from .\&ljcconfig).\&
.PP
.RE
\fBMQTT_PORT\fR
.RS 4
MQTT broker port (default: 1883).\&
.PP
.RE
.SH FILES
.PP
\fB.\&ljcconfig\fR
.RS 4
Repository configuration file created by \fBljc init\fR.\&
.PP
.RE
\fBregistry.\&yaml\fR
.RS 4
Local data registry definitions.\&
.PP
.RE
\fBjobs/\fR
.RS 4
Job source directories.\&
.PP
.RE
\fBdist/\fR
.RS 4
Built packages (.\&ljc files).\&
.PP
.RE
.SH EXIT STATUS
.PP
\fB0\fR
.RS 4
Success.\&
.PP
.RE
\fB1\fR
.RS 4
General error.\&
.PP
.RE
\fB>1\fR
.RS 4
Job exit code (when using \fBexec --wait\fR).\&
.PP
.RE
